          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何以见得哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有一日金钏姐午倦倚枕，"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恰逢着宝二爷来省夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "便来势向我姐戏谑调情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他因见夫人睡午窗人静"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，竟有这等事！后来怎么样哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再不想将夫人猛然惊醒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "反说道我姐姐勾引爷们。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，真真冤枉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有冤枉在后头呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惹动了夫人嗔大施家法，"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "立刻要将我姐赶出府门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那宝二爷他便该从旁搭救才是呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，再休提起！"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提起了此话痛伤心，"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝二爷真是负心人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "竟然一溜自逃奔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她羞愧难禁玉殒香消一缕魂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当时非但不搭救"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因此我姐才投井"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就是宝二爷的不是啦，难怪妹妹你恨他呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人生寿夭原天命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂能无故怨他人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又何至金簪落井竟成真。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝二爷倘若非薄幸"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "往事不必重提。你看前面离“怡红院”不远，你我送汤去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝二爷倘若非薄幸"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绿沉沉声寂寂怡红院进，"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心恹恹泪涟涟痛姐情深。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "劝玉妹释悲怀休提往事，"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没奈何举罗巾权拭啼痕。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（白玉钏、黄莺儿同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
