    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二婆子",
        "白玉钏",
        "薛宝钗",
        "袭人",
        "贾宝玉",
        "黄莺儿"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（袭人扶贾宝玉同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自那日为金钏受人诘叱，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "触怒了老严亲雷霆大发。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "反累了众姐妹暗自嗟呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倚茜窗思旧事独对庭花。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄莺儿 （内同白） 走哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（白玉钏、黄莺儿同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绕曲径寻回廊小院人静，"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "捧莲碗移玉趾微荡画裙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄莺儿、白玉钏同进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "给二爷请安！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道是谁？原来是玉钏、莺儿两位姐姐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（白玉钏不理。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位姐姐请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷在上，哪有我们的座位！"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫你坐下，你就坐下，不用客气，管什么爷不爷的哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着啊，你自管坐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是断断不敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，袭人姐姐，陪莺儿姐姐外边去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袭人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹随我来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（袭人、黄莺儿同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊玉钏姐姐，你一向可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "左不过是奴才，可有什么好不好的哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这汤是哪个叫你送来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "左不过是太太、奶奶们罢啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳姐姐，将汤递与我吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不当这个差使。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好姐姐，递我一递，我两腿疼痛，难以起身。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（白玉钏不理。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐一定不肯方便，少不得我自己来端。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉起身，痛。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她那里负气儿扬扬不睬，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我待要取羹汤疼痛难挨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "似这般现世报令人难耐，"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我只得取羹汤与你消灾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这才是自作自受，别叫我瞧不起你啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（白玉钏取汤递与贾宝玉喝。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，好难吃！"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿弥陀佛！这样东西还说不好吃，真是罪过！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "委实难吃。不信你来尝一尝，便知道了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（白玉钏尝。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你尝过了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尝过啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好吃不好吃呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好吃得很。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原本好吃呦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我倒上了他的当啦。你说好吃不是？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。我说好吃得很。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我可不给你吃啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好姐姐，给我一点吃吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我偏不给。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赏我一点吃吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "偏不赏，偏不赏！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（白玉钏递汤又缩回，贾宝玉央求。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呃！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二婆子暗同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二婆子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "给宝二爷请安！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（白玉钏失手摔碗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，姐姐可曾烫了手么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "白玉钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我倒没有烫手，你瞧瞧你自己吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（白玉钏下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，原来我倒烫着了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二婆子同背身。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二婆子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天下真有这样呆子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二人可是傅府来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "二婆子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秋芳小姐，在家做些什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "二婆子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无非是吟诗写字。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。也是一个聪明的女子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二婆子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。告辞！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，袭人姐姐哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（袭人上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "袭人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听二爷唤，急忙到床前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袭人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "替我送送二位婆婆，烦劳回府致意秋芳小姐，说我病体已好，诸多费心便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳致意秋芳姐，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "道我贱恙已将痊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二婆子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二婆子同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，莺儿姐姐哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄莺儿上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小识同心结，忽听唤金莺。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷唤我何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请你来此，非为别事，前次见你所打之络，巧妙非常。今日无事，烦劳与我打"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上几个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个容易，但不知二爷您要打什么花纹，何种颜色？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，这个倒把我问住了。你每样与我打上几个就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄莺儿笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呦，那可打不了那么多。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "究竟有什么花样，请姐姐说与我知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方胜、连环、必定如意、万字不断、象眼、椒纹、花云流露、分瓣梅花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好了，好了，你说的太多，我听也听不清楚，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我只问你上次与三姑娘打的是什么花样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那叫分瓣攒心梅花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着啊，就是那个便好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此待我打起来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄莺儿打络。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄莺儿在怡红晴窗小住，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手理着五色丝巧结网络。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊莺儿姐姐，你好一双巧手。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝二爷他一旁温存与我，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猛然间一件事兜在心头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊莺儿姐姐，我想你家小姐与你这样一对神仙似的人儿，将来不知何人有福，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方能消受。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷休要取笑，想我乃是婢女，下贱之人，何足挂齿。只是我们小姐她——"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么样啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真要有福气的，方能消受？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何以见得呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷你有所不知，她有几件人家没有的好处。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么好处，倒要请教。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不说啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休要害臊，到底是什么好处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他那里软意儿苦苦问我，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这时候倒叫我怎能不说。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄莺儿出门看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然是无一人何妨饶舌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷，你既真心问我，若不说出来，也对不住你。但是一件！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我告诉你，你可不许告诉别人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个自然。我是一定不告诉别人的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们小姐她呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她有什么好处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她呀，她呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她到底有什么好处啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛宝钗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闲无事来至在绛芸轩下，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又只见黄莺儿巧结梅花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莺儿，你在此打络作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄莺儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是宝二爷叫我打的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊宝姐姐，是我烦她打的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打此何用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是姐姐提起，我倒忘怀了。到底作什么用呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我到想起一个用处来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "作何用处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我寻几根乌丝珠线，打一个络子，把那块宝玉络起来，你道好是不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉拍手。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙极，妙极。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梅花结络闲无事，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "芳心指点到通灵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉、薛宝钗",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉、薛宝钗同下。）"
        }
      ],
